        <title>JAPR Engine</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/resources/JAPREngine.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is my first graphic engine I did as final project of the subject “Visual Programming Fundamentals”. It is done using C++ and Open GL 3.3v.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My Voxel engine has: 
- SSAO
- Procedural Generation
- TextureArray 
- Shadow mapping&lt;/p&gt;

